<item>
            <title>[PIG-1394] POCombinerPackage hold too much memory for InternalCachedBag</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-1394</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In POCombinerPackage, we create bunch of InternalCachedBag, the number of which is the number of algebraic UDFs we use. However, when we create InternalCachedBag, we use the default construct which assume we only create 1 InternalCachedBag in the system. It turns out we reserve way to much memory to InternalCachedBag.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
